#: ../../../customisation/toc.md:1
msgid "Hiding Contents sidebar"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/toc.md:7
msgid ""
"Furo supports hiding the \"Contents\" sidebar (right), and does so "
"automatically for any pages that don't have any inner headings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/toc.md:9
msgid ""
"To explicitly hide it on a specific page, `hide-toc` can be set in the [File-"
"Wide metadata][sphinx-file-wide-metadata] for that page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/toc.md:12
msgid ""
":hide-toc:\n"
"\n"
"[page contents]\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/toc.md:20
msgid ""
"---\n"
"hide-toc: true\n"
"---\n"
"\n"
"[page contents]\n"
msgstr ""
